Subject: [PATCH v2 13/14] spi: bcmbca-hsspi: Add driver for newer HSSPI controller
Date:   Tue, 24 Jan 2023 14:12:16 -0800
Message-Id: <20230124221218.341511-14-william.zhang@broadcom.com>
